<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/983875-i-am-listening-to-the-audiobook-and-i">I am listening to the audiobook and I thought I heard the reader (as Rube) say, &quot;Chaos follows belligerance into office&quot; which of course made me reflect on politics. Did I hear this correctly? Can anyone with the printed text confirm this? It is likely to be found around chapter 5 or 6.</a>
</div>
